.SH NAME
drm_crtc_wait_one_vblank \- wait for one vblank
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" drm_crtc_wait_one_vblank
.BI "(struct drm_crtc *crtc "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc" 12
DRM crtc
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This waits for one vblank to pass on \fIcrtc\fP, using the irq driver interfaces.
It is a failure to call this when the vblank irq for \fIcrtc\fP is disabled, e.g.
due to lack of driver support or because the crtc is off.
